// castle
    TriviaData[22][0] = "I have buttons or a zipper. You don't need me in the summer. Hang me in your front closet. I'll protect you from a  cold wind. I have pockets and sometimes a belt. Am I a pair of shorts?"
// coat
    TriviaData[23][0] = "I am multi-coloured. I appear after a storm. People always point at me. Everyone takes my picture. Legend says there is gold at the bottom of me. Am I a rainbow?"
// rainbow
    TriviaData[24][0] = "I am a delicious treat. Lick me with your tongue. I come in a bowl or a cone. Don't eat me too slowly. One of my flavours is vanilla. Am I soup?"
// ice cream
    TriviaData[25][0] = "I'm a pretend animal. I have four paws. I'm stuffed with fluff. Please take me to bed with you. Hug me if you have a bad dream. Am I a teddy bear?"
// teddy bear
